  "markup": "\u003Cp style=\u0022mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto;\u0022 class=\u0022MsoNormal\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EPurpose:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none;\u0022\u003E To establish clear and consistent guidelines for providing employment references for former employees and requesting references for prospective hires, ensuring fairness, compliance with privacy regulations, and protection from liability.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto;\u0022 class=\u0022MsoNormal\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EProcedure:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Col start=\u00221\u0022 type=\u00221\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cli class=\u0022MsoNormal\u0022 style=\u0022mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo1; tab-stops: list 1.0in;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EProviding References for Former Employees\u003C/strong\u003E:\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli class=\u0022MsoNormal\u0022 style=\u0022mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-list: l0 level3 lfo1; tab-stops: list 1.5in;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EAuthorized Spokesperson:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none;\u0022\u003E All requests for employment verification or references for current or former employees must be directed exclusively to the Human Resources Department. Individual managers or supervisors are generally \u003Cem\u003Enot\u003C/em\u003E authorized to provide references.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli class=\u0022MsoNormal\u0022 style=\u0022mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-list: l0 level3 lfo1; tab-stops: list 1.5in;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ELimited Information:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none;\u0022\u003E To protect both the Company and the former employee, Neumo\u2019s policy is to provide only neutral, factual information in response to reference requests. This typically includes: Confirmation of dates of employment, last position held. (Optionally, with employee\u0027s written consent: last salary/wage rate).\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli class=\u0022MsoNormal\u0022 style=\u0022mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-list: l0 level3 lfo1; tab-stops: list 1.5in;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ENo Opinions or Performance Details\u003C/strong\u003E:\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none;\u0022\u003E Neumo will not provide information regarding an individual\u0027s performance, reasons for departure, or any subjective opinions, unless legally compelled or with specific, written authorization from the former employee.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli class=\u0022MsoNormal\u0022 style=\u0022mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-list: l0 level3 lfo1; tab-stops: list 1.5in;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EWritten Requests Preferred\u003C/strong\u003E:\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none;\u0022\u003E While we may verbally confirm employment, we generally prefer and may require all reference requests to be submitted in writing.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n\u003Cli class=\u0022MsoNormal\u0022 style=\u0022mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo1; tab-stops: list 1.0in;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ERequesting References for Prospective Hires\u003C/strong\u003E:\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli class=\u0022MsoNormal\u0022 style=\u0022mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-list: l0 level3 lfo1; tab-stops: list 1.5in;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EStandard Practice:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none;\u0022\u003E As part of our hiring process, Neumo will conduct reference checks for prospective employees to verify information provided during the application process and to gain insights into their past performance and conduct.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli class=\u0022MsoNormal\u0022 style=\u0022mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-list: l0 level3 lfo1; tab-stops: list 1.5in;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EAuthorized Personnel:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none;\u0022\u003E Reference checks will be conducted by Human Resources or designated hiring managers.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli class=\u0022MsoNormal\u0022 style=\u0022mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-list: l0 level3 lfo1; tab-stops: list 1.5in;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EConsent:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none;\u0022\u003E We will obtain consent from applicants to contact their references.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli class=\u0022MsoNormal\u0022 style=\u0022mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-list: l0 level3 lfo1; tab-stops: list 1.5in;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EJob-Related Inquiries:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none;\u0022\u003E All reference inquiries will be job-related and non-discriminatory, focusing on relevant skills, experience, work habits, and professional conduct.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli class=\u0022MsoNormal\u0022 style=\u0022mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-list: l0 level3 lfo1; tab-stops: list 1.5in;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EConfidentiality:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none;\u0022\u003E Information gathered during reference checks will be treated confidentially and used solely for employment decision-making purposes.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n\u003Cli class=\u0022MsoNormal\u0022 style=\u0022mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo1; tab-stops: list 1.0in;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EEmployee Inquiries about References\u003C/strong\u003E:\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none;\u0022\u003E Employees should direct any questions or requests regarding providing references for external organizations to the Human Resources Department. Employees should not provide personal references on company letterhead or imply company endorsement for personal references.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli class=\u0022MsoNormal\u0022 style=\u0022mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo1; tab-stops: list 1.0in;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EConsequences of Violation\u003C/strong\u003E:\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none;\u0022\u003E Failure to adhere to this policy regarding providing references may result in disciplinary action, as unauthorized disclosures can lead to legal complications for the Company.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ol\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E"
}]]></Value>
